         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">31/3/93 ¶  ¶ It is very pleasing for me, esteemed Mr Tepper, that you intend to assist  ¶ me ¶  in the completion of the  ¶ Flora australiensis ¶ . ¶  Would you be so kind in occasional leisure hours ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">93.03.31a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by Tepper: 'Reply 6.4.93'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>31/3/93</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es ist für mich recht erfreulich, geehrter Herr Tepper, dass Sie </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">mir</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> beistehen wollen in der Vollendung der Flora Australiensis. Würden Sie so freundlich sein, in gelegentlichen Musse-Stunden aus Ihrem Herbarium solche Standorte auszucopiren, als noch nicht vorkommend in den mir zugesandten Exemplaren, u auch sonst niederzuschreiben, was Sie über die Verbreitung von Ihnen wohl u </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">sicher</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> bekannten Arten </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">erinnern</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">. Solche Data sollen dann (O.T) bezeichnet in der Ergänzungs Band aufgenommen werden.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Kein Suppl. Band von Benth. &amp; Hook. gen ist ebensowenig erschienen noch versprochen, obwohl ein solcher mehr nöthig wäre als einer für die Fl. </seg>Australiensis</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">31/3/93</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is very pleasing for me, esteemed Mr Tepper, that you intend to assist <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">me</hi>
               </seg> in the completion of the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Flora australiensis</seg>.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>M was preparing a supplement to Bentham (1863-78), but it was never published; see Clements (1998) and Lucas (2003).</p>
               </note> Would you be so kind in occasional leisure hours as to copy out such localities from your herbarium as still not occurring in the specimens sent to me, and also otherwise to write down what you <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">remember</hi>
               </seg> about the distribution of species well and <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">reliably</hi>
               </seg> known to you. Such data, indicated (O.T), will then be included in the supplementary volume.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">A supplementary volume of Bentham &amp; Hooker's <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Genera</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Bentham &amp; Hooker (1862-83).</p>
               </note> is neither published nor promised, although such would be more necessary than one for the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Flora australiensis</seg>.</p>
         </div>
